article.headline: Becker scores 31 as Air Force knocks off William & Mary 80-71 in OT
article.description: — Beau Becker scored 31 points as Air Force beat William & Mary 80-71 in overtime on Friday night.
article.linkText: Becker scores 31 as Air Force knocks off William & Mary 80-71 in OT
article.story: AIR FORCE ACADEMY, Colo. -- — Beau Becker scored 31 points as Air Force beat William & Mary 80-71 in overtime on Friday night. Becker also had five rebounds for the Falcons (3-2). Ethan Taylor scored 24 points and added six rebounds. Kellan Boylan had eight points. The Tribe (2-3) were led in scoring by Trey Moss, who finished with 20 points, seven rebounds and four assists. Gabe Dorsey added 12 points for William & Mary. Jack Karasinski also recorded 11 points and seven rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
